OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy at times across
OL,6,Fsouthern coasts with some further
OL,7,Fshowery rain towards Cornwall and
OL,8,Flater into Devon. Largely dry with
OL,9,Fsunny spells elsewhere, and feeling
OL,10,Fwarm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRather cloudy overnight with
OL,13,Fshowery outbreaks of rain slowly
OL,14,Fedging southwards during the night.
OL,15,FRather breezy in places, particularly
OL,16,Fnear coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
