OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAny remaining outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain clearing the south coast early
OL,7,FSunday. Otherwise a largely dry and
OL,8,Fbright day with sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Feeling pleasant in the
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,13,FUnsettled and cool next week, with
OL,14,Frain or showers affecting much of the
OL,15,Fcountry. Some spells of sunshine in
OL,16,Fthe mix too, but feeling chilly, with
OL,17,Fa risk of frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
